    Enum containing references to various packet types sent by the game client.

    - IF Button types are sent when any of the normal buttons on newer interfaces are clicked - Move game click is the packet that the client sends upon clicking on a game square to move towards it. - Event Mouse click packets are written whenever the player clicks anywhere on their client, whether it be dead space, or any entity in-game
